= Sherminal
Asynchronous shared termial based on xterm.js and tornado.

== Building
. `pip3 install -r requirements.txt`
. `npm install` in ./client
. `npm start` in ./client ro serve the client
. `sudo python3 server/server.py` to run the app
. copy or link files in utilites to a place like /usr/local/bin

NOTE: The app uses `chroot` and `mount` for user isolation and because of this needs to be ran with superuser privileges.

== Dependencies
. Python 3.6
